{
  "stem": "16214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by that time, I was-- I was nine years old already, which means I was three and a half years with my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And yet the feeling, you know, that these are Jews, you know, and I am not, was always there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, I was angry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was angry that here I'm coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no-- I mean, normally in any household, as you very well know, when you have another child coming along, the older one feels threatened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And here, not only am I so confused with everything what's happening around me, but on top of that my mother is going to have another child.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So of course I was jealous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was upset.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was staying with my father alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother was away, so it was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember vividly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People were starting to go to church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I wanted to go to church, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father was trying to help to dress me, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was some shoes that I would not want to wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because this was a pair of shoes that actually he made them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's incredible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This man could do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not only all sorts of, you know, mechanical things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But he prepared-- he made shoes for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because it was difficult during that time in post-war Poland to have a good pair of leather shoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he made them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I refused to put them on, you know, put them on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he tried to force them on me, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was holding my leg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And tried to put those shoes on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I started screaming, the Jew is killing me!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The Jew is killing me!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now we lived right in front, as I showed you, right in front of the church.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
